{"tid":2024391,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[DC又贏]《正義聯盟 Justice League》導剪版終將登上世人眼前？","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T15:12:09.000Z","uid":249940,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3c2880721d35251976db5b07d6955bc48ddc0e","tid":2024391,"uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"近期根據 Heroic Hollywood 的獨家報導指出，Zack Snyder 曾在今年初進行《正義聯盟》導演剪輯版的試鏡，不少 DC 與 Warner Bros. 高層亦有參加，已知情報人士表示有些事情正在發生與討論中；而過去不少媒體就曾評斷如要尋一途徑釋出導演剪輯版，即將登場的 HBO Max 或將是最佳選擇？！<br />\n<br />\n不少人認為 HBO Max 的片單陣容比起 Disney+ 相對薄弱，其片單的吸引力仍然不夠大，或是頗有看頭的作品皆仍在製作前期階段，因此趁勢釋出《正義聯盟》導演剪輯版何嘗不可呢？對吧，各位 DC 粉絲們？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2020/5/zack-snyder-justice-league-cut-get-released-hbo-max-dc-warner-bros%3famp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F5%2Fzack-snyder-justice-league-cut-get-released-hbo-max-dc-warner-bros%253famp%3D1&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=0c179814\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2020/5/zack-snyder-justice-league-cut-get-released-hbo-max-dc-warner-bros%3famp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3076184bdeef6173a84e9400432ed2c0328f8c","tid":2024391,"uid":187368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"好撚想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee84b347b1b576fa138a08c009ac798cae5ef319","tid":2024391,"u